{"tid":2300669,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旅議會財困裁員10多人 中高層減薪2成","createTime":"2020-11-25T16:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T17:24:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec757b4ca89939f00726debbd0db1467843c8c6d","tid":2300669,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WsYBw3puAyJrMuL4rmKx2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/16NQJ.ZOT_8TTB2p9CerTw--~B/aD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/4229d1f5623f308402e3a241a3ed5e7c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWsYBw3puAyJrMuL4rmKx2A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F16NQJ.ZOT_8TTB2p9CerTw--~B%2FaD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F4229d1f5623f308402e3a241a3ed5e7c&h=afdfa435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情持續重創旅遊業，依賴旅行社印花徵費及徵收內地團客人頭費的旅遊業議會面臨財困，今日(25日)即日遣散10多人，中層員工亦要減薪2成，辦事處部分場地亦退租，估計可省減約100萬港元的開支。旅議會主席黃進達形容是無奈的決定，稱目前會節流，暫未見到其他解決的辦法。<br />\n<br />\n黃進達表示，旅議會原來有約50名員工，遣散10多人後員工減至30多人，留下的員工需要減薪，但主要是中高層，基層員工不受影響。他指議會現存儲備可捱多一年，待旅遊業監管局接手旅議會的工作。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，未知疫情何時完結，對議會未來收入未敢樂觀。但議會仍會保持對會員及旅客的服務，保留應有的員工人數。"},{"pid":"ca9b2efc25b688256908c24d495621d19bf6cce3","tid":2300669,"uid":36993,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:59:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾吸血機構早執早着<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8202602c2d21012866af6929f9fdd857a970497","tid":2300669,"uid":39383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"收埋d 污糟錢咁耐, 有排都未還突"},{"pid":"f415c146f7606d9b487df903464ff58815dd88fc","tid":2300669,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:15:0